# 尝试进行变量拆分，把except的问题存入error中
room, hall, kitchen, toilet, price, floor1, floor2, h, area = [], [], [], [], [], [], [], [], []
error = []

for n in range(len(data)):
    try:
        txt1 = data['房屋户型'][n]
        temp1 = re.findall(r'(.)室(.)厅(.)厨(.)卫', txt1, re.S)[0]
        room.append(int(temp1[0]))
        hall.append(int(temp1[1]))
        kitchen.append(int(temp1[2]))
        toilet.append(int(temp1[3]))

        txt2 = data['价格'][n]
        price.append(int(re.findall(r'(.*?)元/平米', txt2, re.S)[0]))

        txt3 = data['所在楼层'][n]
        floor1.append(re.findall(r'(.)楼层', txt3, re.S)[0])
        floor2.append(int(re.findall('共(.*?)层', txt3)[0]))

        txt4 = data['建筑面积'][n]
        area.append(float(re.findall(r'(.*?)㎡.*', txt4, re.S)[0]))
    except:
        error.append(n)

error = []

for n in range(len(data)):
    try:
        txt1 = data['房屋户型'][n]
        temp1 = re.findall(r'(.)室(.)厅(.)厨(.)卫', txt1, re.S)[0]
        room.append(int(temp1[0]))
        hall.append(int(temp1[1]))
        kitchen.append(int(temp1[2]))
        toilet.append(int(temp1[3]))

        txt2 = data['价格'][n]
        price.append(int(re.findall(r'(.*?)元/平米', txt2, re.S)[0]))

        txt3 = data['所在楼层'][n]
        floor1.append(re.findall(r'(.)楼层', txt3, re.S)[0])
        floor2.append(int(re.findall('共(.*?)层', txt3)[0]))

        txt4 = data['建筑面积'][n]

orientation_df = pd.concat([pd.Series(row['index'],row['房屋朝向'].split(' ')) for _, row in df.iterrows()]).reset_index()
orientation_df.columns = ['orientation','index']
orientation_df_clean = orientation_df[orientation_df['orientation'].isin(['东','南','西','北','东南','西南','东北','西北'])]
orientation_df_clean['value'] = 1
orientation_df_p = orientation_df_clean.pivot_table(index='index',columns=['orientation'],values=['value']).reset_index()
orientation_df_p.columns = ['index']+[i[1] for i in list(orientation_df_p.columns)][1:]

#合并
df = df.merge(orientation_df_p,on='index',how='left')
df = df.fillna(0)

# stratified sampling
# 保证训练集和测试集的各城市占比、装修情况占比是一样的
from sklearn.model_selection import StratifiedShuffleSplit

split = StratifiedShuffleSplit(n_splits=1, 
                               test_size=0.2, 
                               random_state=42)

for train_index, test_index in split.split(df, df["城市"]):
    train_set = df.loc[train_index]
    test_set = df.loc[test_index]
    
print(test_set["城市"].value_counts() / len(test_set))
print(test_set["装修情况"].value_counts() / len(test_set))

# 随机森林
# 以下使用的参数是使用Grid_Search进行优化后的参数

rf = RandomForestRegressor(criterion='mse', 
                           bootstrap=True, 
                           max_features='auto', 
                           max_depth=None, 
                           min_samples_split=2, 
                           max_leaf_nodes=None, 
                           n_estimators=10, 
                           max_samples = None,
                           verbose=2,
                           min_samples_leaf=1, 
                           n_jobs = -1)

# max_depth树的深度；n_estimators树的棵树
rf = rf.fit(x_train, y_train)
y_train_pred = rf.predict(x_train)
y_test_pred = rf.predict(x_test)
# 模型评估
rf.score(x_train, y_train)
train_score_rf = rf.score(x_train, y_train)
test_score_rf = rf.score(x_test, y_test)
mse_rf = mean_squared_error(y_test, y_test_pred)
evs_rf = explained_variance_score(y_test, y_test_pred)
r_rf = r2_score(y_test, y_test_pred)
mae_rf = mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_test_pred)
print(train_score_rf, test_score_rf, r_rf, mse_rf, evs_rf, mae_rf)
print("randomforest模型评估--训练集：")
print('训练r^2:', rf.score(x_train, y_train))
print('均方差', mean_squared_error(y_train, y_train_pred))
print('绝对差', mean_absolute_error(y_train, y_train_pred))
print('解释度', explained_variance_score(y_train, y_train_pred))
print("randomforest模型评估--验证集：")
print('验证r^2:', rf.score(x_test, y_test))
print('均方差', mean_squared_error(y_test, y_test_pred))
print('绝对差', mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_test_pred))
print('解释度', explained_variance_score(y_test, y_test_pred))

# GridSearch 可视化
filepath = '/Users/arwen/Downloads'
fig_name = 'cv_heatmap.png'
fig_path = filepath + '/' + fig_name
max_depth_list = list(clf.cv_results_['param_max_depth'].data)
estimators_list = list(clf.cv_results_['param_n_estimators'].data)

sns.set_style("whitegrid")
plt.figure(figsize=(16,6))
plt.subplot(1,2,1)
data = pd.DataFrame(data={'Estimators':estimators_list, 'Max Depth':max_depth_list, 'AUC':clf.cv_results_['mean_train_score']})
data = data.pivot(index='Estimators', columns='Max Depth', values='AUC')
sns.heatmap(data, annot=True, cmap="YlGn").set_title('AUC for Training data')
plt.subplot(1,2,2)

data = pd.DataFrame(data={'Estimators':estimators_list, 'Max Depth':max_depth_list, 'AUC':clf.cv_results_['mean_test_score']})
data = data.pivot(index='Estimators', columns='Max Depth', values='AUC')
fig = sns.heatmap(data, annot=True, cmap="YlGnBu").set_title('AUC for Test data')
plt.show()

scatter_fig = fig.get_figure()
scatter_fig.savefig(fig_path, dpi = 400)
